data.revised_prompt: Imagine a landscape image inspired by late 19th century romantic art, capturing the essence of a futuristic paladin-style alien military. These extraterrestrial beings, armored in advanced technology, stand ready to maintain order in an anomalous landscape. Their weaponry shows indications of advanced civilizations, and their stature emits a sense of authority and control. For the landscape, imagine the surreal elements of space - unusual land formations, a wide range of coiling misty colors, and star-studded skies that pay homage to the techniques used in traditional oil paintings. Remember, this is about balancing the futuristic elements with the distinctly vintage-style painting techniques.
